{
  "stem": "17001.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 166.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were the one who were overseeing that how many people could go up on one [POLISH], how many people could go.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were the one who were bringing the bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were the one who were bringing the [HUNGARIAN], the-- the soup.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sometimes they were asking some of us that we should go and help them and bring it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So at one-- when-- while we were breaking the rocks, I seen that front of the kitchen on the right side, there is like gray canvas.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this covered off, and this lined up there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I stoop down and I crawled down, and I was going there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I lifted up the-- the grayish cover, and I seen some bones in there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Bones like this, this-- this way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I grab three of them, and I was running.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when I get to the rocks where my sisters, both my sisters were, I started to break the bone up and we took all the-- the marrow, and we were eating it, licking it with our finger, and we were eating it.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then meantime, we were talking and wondering what kind of a bone is that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, how-- how did this bone get there?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm sorry to say that, but our conclusion was that they were bringing in the limbs of the bodies from the crematorium and they had cooked it into the soup as meat, and these were the bones that they left there.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At one occasion when I was stealing the bone, by that time we got smart.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were saving the bread from the night before, because we don't get-- we don't want to get sick from this marrow, this fat stuff.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were saving the bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
